splay: inline-flex; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 1px; color: var(--acc,#4f7ef7);\"><svg data-dc-tpl=\"531\" width=\"17\" height=\"17\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path data-dc-tpl=\"532\" d=\"M5 12.5l4.5 4.5L19 7.5\"></path></svg></span>Full Engineering Decision Graph</div>\n          <div data-dc-tpl=\"533\" style=\"display: flex; gap: 10px;\"><span data-dc-tpl=\"534\" style=\"display: inline-flex; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 1px; color: var(--acc,#4f7ef7);\"><svg data-dc-tpl=\"535\" width=\"17\" height=\"17\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path data-dc-tpl=\"536\" d=\"M5 12.5l4.5 4.5L19 7.5\"></path></svg></span>Company rule enforcement</div>\n          <div data-dc-tpl=\"537\" style=\"display: flex; gap: 10px;\"><span data-dc-tpl=\"538\" style=\"display: inline-flex; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 1px; color: var(--acc,#4f7ef7);\"><svg data-dc-tpl=\"539\" width=\"17\" height=\"17\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path data-dc-tpl=\"540\" d=\"M5 12.5l4.5 4.5L19 7.5\"></path></svg></span>MCP server + API access</div>\n          <div data-dc-tpl=\"541\" style=\"display: flex; gap: 10px;\"><span data-dc-tpl=\"542\" style=\"display: inline-flex; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 1px; color: var(--acc,#4f7ef7);\"><svg data-dc-tpl=\"543\" width=\"17\" height=\"17\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path data-dc-tpl=\"544\" d=\"M5 12.5l4.5 4.5L19 7.5\"></path></svg></span>Slack, Notion, Jira, GitHub</div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div data-dc-tpl=\"545\" data-reveal=\"\" style=\"padding: 30px 28px; border-radius: 20px; border: 1px solid rgba(28, 20, 45, 0.08); background: linear-gradient(rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.66), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.01));\">\n        <div data-dc-tpl=\"546\" style=\"font-family: var(--font-display), sans-serif; font-weight: 600; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(36, 29, 51);\">Enterprise</div>\n        <div data-dc-tpl=\"547\" style=\"margin-top: 6px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(111, 106, 125);\">For orgs with strict requirements</div>\n        <div data-dc-tpl=\"548\" style=\"margin-top: 22px; display: flex; align-items: baseline; gap: 6px;\"><span data-dc-tpl=\"549\" style=\"font-family: var(--font-display), sans-serif; font-weight: 600; font-size: 44px; color: rgb(27, 23, 38);\">Custom</span></div>\n        <a data-dc-tpl=\"550\" href=\"/contact?topic=sales\" style=\"display: block; text-align: center; margin-top: 22px; padding: 12px; border-radius: 11px; border: 1px solid rgba(28, 20, 45, 0.11); background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6); color: rgb(86, 81, 99); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500; font-size: 14.5px;\">Talk to sales</a>\n        <div data-dc-tpl=\"551\" style=\"margin-top: 22px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 11px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(107, 102, 120);\">\n          <div data-dc-tpl=\"552\" style=\"display: flex; gap: 10px;\"><span data-dc-tpl=\"553\" style=\"display: inline-flex; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 1px; color: var(--acc,#4f7ef7);\"><svg data-dc-tpl=\"554\" width=\"17\" height=\"17\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path data-dc-tpl=\"555\" d=\"M5 12.5l4.5 4.5L19 7.5\"></path></svg></span>Self-hosted / VPC</div>\n          <div data-dc-tpl=\"556\" style=\"display: flex; gap: 10px;\"><span data-dc-tpl=\"557\" style=\"display: inline-flex; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 1px; color: var(--acc,#4f7ef7);\"><svg data-dc-tpl=\"558\" width=\"17\" height=\"17\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path data-dc-tpl=\"559\" d=\"M5 12.5l4.5 4.5L19 7.5\"></path></svg></span>SSO, SCIM, audit logs</div>\n          <div data-dc-tpl=\"560\" style=\"display: flex; gap: 10px;\"><span data-dc-tpl=\"561\" style=\"display: inline-flex; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 1px; color: var(--acc,#4f7ef7);\"><svg data-dc-tpl=\"562\" width=\"17\" height=\"17\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path data-dc-tpl=\"563\" d=\"M5 12.5l4.5 4.5L19 7.5\"></path></svg></span>Custom integrations</div>\n          <div data-dc-tpl=\"564\" style=\"display: flex; gap: 10px;\"><span data-dc-tpl=\"565\" style=\"display: inline-flex; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 1px; color: var(--acc,#4f7ef7);\"><svg data-dc-tpl=\"566\" width=\"17\" height=\"17\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path data-dc-tpl=\"567\" d=\"M5 12.5l4.5 4.5L19 7.5\"></path></svg></span>Dedicated engineer</div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  \n  <section data-dc-tpl=\"568\" id=\"faq\" style=\"position: relative; z-index: 1; max-width: 820px; margin: 0px auto; padding: 130px 24px 0px;\">\n    <div data-dc-tpl=\"569\" data-reveal=\"\" style=\"text-align: center; font-family: var(--font-mono), monospace; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.16em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--acc2,#7fb0f2);\">08 — FAQ</div>\n    <h2 data-dc-tpl=\"570\" data-reveal=\"\" style=\"font-family: var(--font-display), sans-serif; font-weight: 600; font-size: clamp(30px, 4.4vw, 50px); line-height: 1.06; letter-spacing: -0.025em; margin: 16px 0px 0px; text-align: center; color: rgb(27, 23, 38);\">Questions, answered</h2>\n    <div data-dc-tpl=\"571\" style=\"margin-top: 40px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 12px;\">\n      \n        <div data-dc-tpl=\"573\" data-reveal=\"\" style=\"border-radius: 15px; border: 1px solid rgba(28, 20, 45, 0.08); background: linear-gradient(rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.66), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5)); overflow: hidden;\">\n          <button data-dc-tpl=\"574\" style=\"width: 100%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: 16px; padding: 20px 22px; background: transparent; border-width: medium; border-style: none; border-color: currentcolor; border-image: initial; cursor: pointer; text-align: left; color: rgb(36, 29, 51); font-family: var(--font-display), sans-serif; font-weight: 500; font-size: 17px;\">\n            <span data-dc-tpl=\"575\"><span class=\"sc-interp\">Does this replace Claude Code or Cursor?</span></span>\n            <span data-dc-tpl=\"576\" style=\"font-family: var(--font-inter-tight), sans-serif; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 300; color: rgb(79, 126, 247); transition: transform 0.3s; flex-shrink: 0; transform: rotate(45deg);\">+</span>\n          </button>\n          \n            <div data-dc-tpl=\"578\" style=\"padding: 0px 22px 22px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.62; color: rgb(86, 81, 99);\"><span class=\"sc-interp\">No — Slovey sits beneath them. Your agents keep writing code exactly as they do today; we review every change against your company’s context and send fixes back before anything is committed.</span></div>\n          \n        </div>\n      \n        <div data-dc-tpl=\"573\" data-reveal=\"\" style=\"border-radius: 15px; border: 1px solid rgba(28, 20, 45, 0.08); background: linear-gradient(rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.66), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5)); overflow: hidden;\">\n          <button data-dc-tpl=\"574\" style=\"width: 100%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: 16px; padding: 20px 22px; background: transparent; border-width: medium; border-style: none; border-color: currentcolor; border-image: initial; cursor: pointer; text-align: left; color: rgb(36, 29, 51); font-family: var(--font-display), sans-serif; font-weight: 500; font-size: 17px;\">\n            <span data-dc-tpl=\"575\"><span class=\"sc-interp\">How does it learn my company?</span></span>\n            <span data-dc-tpl=\"576\" style=\"font-family: var(--font-inter-tight), sans-serif; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 300; color: rgb(117, 112, 127); transition: transform 0.3s; flex-shrink: 0; transform: rotate(0deg);\">+</span>\n          </button>\n          \n        </div>\n      \n        <div data-dc-tpl=\"573\" data-reveal=\"\" style=\"border-radius: 15px; border: 1px solid rgba(28, 20, 45, 0.08); background: linear-gradient(rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.66), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5)); overflow: hidden;\">\n          <button data-dc-tpl=\"574\" style=\"width: 100%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: 16px; padding: 20px 22px; background: transparent; border-width: medium; border-style: none; border-color: currentcolor; border-image: initial; cursor: pointer; text-align: left; color: rgb(36, 29, 51); font-family: var(--font-display), sans-serif; font-weight: 500; font-size: 17px;\">\n            <span data-dc-tpl=\"575\"><span class=\"sc-interp\">Where does my code and data live?</span></span>\n            <span data-dc-tpl=\"576\" style=\"font-family: var(--font-inter-tight), sans-serif; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 300; color: rgb(117, 112, 127); transition: transform 0.3s; flex-shrink: 0; transform: rotate(0deg);\">+</span>\n          </button>\n          \n        </div>\n      \n        <div data-dc-tpl=\"573\" data-reveal=\"\" style=\"border-radius: 15px; border: 1px solid rgba(28, 20, 45, 0.08); background: linear-gradient(rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.66), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5)); overflow: hidden;\">\n          <button data-dc-tpl=\"574\" style=\"width: 100%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: 16px; padding: 20px 22px; background: transparent; border-width: medium; border-style: none; border-color: currentcolor; border-image: initial; cursor: pointer; text-align: left; color: rgb(36, 29, 51); font-family: var(--font-display), sans-serif; font-weight: 500; font-size: 17px;\">\n            <span data-dc-tpl=\"575\"><span class=\"sc-interp\">Which tools does it integrate with?</span></span>\n            <span data-dc-tpl=\"576\" style=\"font-family: var(--font-inter-tight), sans-serif; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 300; color: rgb(117, 112, 127); transition: transform 0.3s; flex-shrink: 0; transform: rotate(0deg);\">+</span>\n          </button>\n          \n        </div>\n      \n        <div data-dc-tpl=\"573\" data-reveal=\"\" style=\"border-radius: 15px; border: 1px solid rgba(28, 20, 45, 0.08); background: linear-gradient(rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.66), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5)); overflow: hidden;\">\n          <button data-dc-tpl=\"574\" style=\"width: 100%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: 16px; padding: 20px 22px; background: transparent; border-width: medium; border-style: none; border-color: currentcolor; border-image: initial; cursor: pointer; text-align: left; color: rgb(36, 29, 51); font-family: var(--font-display), sans-serif; font-weight: 500; font-size: 17px;\">\n            <span data-dc-tpl=\"575\"><span class=\"sc-interp\">How does the MCP server work?</span></span>\n            <span data-dc-tpl=\"576\" style=\"font-family: var(--font-inter-tight), sans-serif; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 300; color: rgb(117, 112, 127); transition: transform 0.3s; flex-shrink: 0; transform: rotate(0deg);\">+</span>\n          </button>\n          \n        </div>\n      \n        <div data-dc-tpl=\"573\" data-reveal=\"\" style=\"border-radius: 15px; border: 1px solid rgba(28, 20, 45, 0.08); background: linear-gradient(rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.66), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5)); overflow: hidden;\">\n          <button data-dc-tpl=\"574\" style=\"width: 100%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: 16px; padding: 20px 22px; background: transparent; border-width: medium; border-s